## SCREEN TRANSITIONS

### Stack Navigation (Forward / Push):
```
Screen A → Screen B
[Screen A slides out left] + [Screen B slides in from right]
```
- Type: SLIDE_IN, direction: LEFT
- Duration: 300-350ms
- Easing: gentle or ease-in-out

### Stack Navigation (Back / Pop):
```
Screen B → Screen A
[Screen B slides out right] + [Screen A slides in from left]
```
- Type: SLIDE_OUT, direction: RIGHT
- Duration: 300-350ms
- Easing: gentle or ease-in-out

### Modal (Open):
```
[Overlay fades in] + [Sheet slides up from bottom]
```
- Type: SLIDE_IN, direction: BOTTOM
- Duration: 350-400ms
- Easing: ease-out or gentle

### Modal (Close):
```
[Sheet slides down] + [Overlay fades out]
```
- Type: SLIDE_OUT, direction: BOTTOM
- Duration: 250-300ms
- Easing: ease-in

### Tab Switch:
```
[Tab A fades out] + [Tab B fades in]
```
- Type: DISSOLVE or SMART_ANIMATE
- Duration: 200-250ms
- Easing: ease-in-out

