## MOTION HIERARCHY

### Elements enter in sequence (stagger):
```
Header:     [====]           ← 0ms delay
Title:       [====]          ← 50ms delay
Subtitle:     [====]         ← 100ms delay
Content:       [====]        ← 150ms delay
CTA:            [====]       ← 200ms delay
```

- Stagger delay: 30-60ms between elements
- Each element: 200-300ms fade + slide up
- Easing: ease-out for each element

### RULE:
> Stagger is SUBTLE. If total delay > 400ms, the user feels slowness.
> Maximum 4-5 elements in stagger. More than that → all together.

