## MOTION ANTI-PATTERNS

| ❌ Wrong | ✅ Correct |
|---|---|
| Animation > 700ms for transition | 300-350ms for most |
| Bounce/overshoot in serious app | Gentle/ease-in-out for professional apps |
| Elements entering from all directions | Consistent direction (left→right for forward) |
| Linear easing for everything | Appropriate easing curves by type |
| Loading animation blocking interaction | Non-blocking loading (skeleton) |
| Animation everywhere without purpose | Animation only where it communicates something |
| Delay before starting to animate | Immediate start (0ms delay) |

